  :context
"Alfred directive 2026-07-19:

 > I want to reframe how we talk about them. I don't want to talk about
 > them as products. But in the framing of computer science and
 > engineering. SG is in there. DEC is in there. Why not Anthropic?
 > Claude isn't a shell script.

 New scheme-book: `book-of-ai-tech-cards`. Engineering-firm register —
 same tone as we'd give DEC, SGI, Xerox PARC, Bell Labs, Sun. Facts
 about AI firms and their contributions to the field. No product
 marketing. No rankings. No recommendations."

